<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.salon.com/politics/war_room/2008/07/22/schiffren/index.html" class="external free" title="http://www.salon.com/politics/war_room/2008/07/22/schiffren/index.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.salon.com/politics/war_room/2008/07/22/schiffren/index.html</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.crooksandliars.com/2008/02/15/foxs-tom-sullivan-compares-obama-to-hitler/" class="external free" title="http://www.crooksandliars.com/2008/02/15/foxs-tom-sullivan-compares-obama-to-hitler/" rel="nofollow">http://www.crooksandliars.com/2008/02/15/foxs-tom-sullivan-compares-obama-to-hitler/</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
